v0.0.19.02 "beta" @Elo
 - Added when fulfilling an order nirn auction house can now split stacks
 - Added when fulfilling an order if the item is not in your inventory you will be notified if its in your bank or your crafting bag
 - You can only fulfill a buy order if the item is in your inventory, bank, or your crafting bag
 - Added WTB to chat click on your buy order in the buy order window- populates to chat
 - Added WTS to chat click on your listing in the listings window- populates to chat
 - Added Buy orders with no price will have a contact player button
 - Added gamepad support (Mailbox)
 - bugfix toggle NAH hotkey
 - bugfix eu relist
 - bugfix eu fulfilling buy orders
 - bugfix on sync


